  "hashtags" : [ ],
  "sections" : [ {
    "type" : "verse",
    "label" : "VERSE 1",
    "lines" : [ {
      "text" : "I am thinking of the rapture in our blessed home on high,",
      "chords" : [ {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 5
      }, {
        "chord" : "G",
        "position" : 52
      } ]
    }, {
      "text" : "When the redeemed are gathering in;",
      "chords" : [ {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 9
      }, {
        "chord" : "A",
        "position" : 32
      } ]
    }, {
      "text" : "How we'll raise the heavenly anthem in that city in the sky,",
      "chords" : [ {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 10
      }, {
        "chord" : "G",
        "position" : 56
      } ]
    }, {
      "text" : "When the redeemed are gathering in.",
      "chords" : [ {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 9
      }, {
        "chord" : "G",
        "position" : 9
      }, {
        "chord" : "A",
        "position" : 22
      }, {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 32
      } ]
    }, {
      "text" : ""
    }, {
      "text" : "When the redeemed are gathering in,",
      "chords" : [ {
        "chord" : "G",
        "position" : 9
      }, {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 32
      } ]
    }, {
      "text" : "Washed like the snow, and free from all sin;",
      "chords" : [ {
        "chord" : "A",
        "position" : 40
      } ]
    }, {
      "text" : "How we will shout, and how we will sing,",
      "chords" : [ {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 35
      } ]
    }, {
      "text" : "When the redeemed are gathering in."
    }, {
      "text" : ""
    }, {
      "text" : "There will be a great procession over on the streets of gold,",
      "chords" : [ {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 16
      }, {
        "chord" : "G",
        "position" : 56
      } ]
    }, {
      "text" : "When the redeemed are gathering in;"
    }, {
      "text" : "O what music, O what singing, o'er the city will be rolled,",
      "chords" : [ {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 39
      } ]
    }, {
      "text" : "When the redeemed are gathering in."
    }, {
      "text" : ""
    }, {
      "text" : "Saints will sing redemption's story with their voices clear and strong,",
      "chords" : [ {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 12
      }, {
        "chord" : "G",
        "position" : 64
      } ]
    }, {
      "text" : "When the redeemed are gathering in;"
    }, {
      "text" : "Then the angels all will listen, For they cannot join that song,",
      "chords" : [ {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 42
      } ]
    }, {
      "text" : "When the redeemed are gathering in."
    }, {
      "text" : ""
    }, {
      "text" : "Then the Saviour will give orders to prepare the banquet board,",
      "chords" : [ {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 9
      }, {
        "chord" : "G",
        "position" : 57
      } ]
    }, {
      "text" : "When the redeemed are gathering in;"
    }, {
      "text" : "And we'll hear His invitation, \"Come, ye blessed of the Lord,\"",
      "chords" : [ {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 41
      } ]
    }, {
      "text" : "When the redeemed are gathering in."
    } ]
  } ]
